# Your memex's .gitignore (memex init writes this as `.gitignore`).
#
# Your DATA is ignored by default, so this memex is safe to publish or share as a structure.
# If you keep this in a PRIVATE repo and want your knowledge versioned, delete the data lines
# below — but NEVER commit secrets.

# ── Knowledge / data (yours) ──
self/*.md
!self/README.md
wiki/**/*.md
!wiki/**/README.md
!wiki/_templates/*.md
history/**/*.md
!history/**/README.md
chats/*.md
!chats/README.md
clients/learning/*.md
!clients/learning/README.md
inbox.md
MAP.md

# ── Secrets & local-only config — NEVER commit ──
*.local.json
.env
.env.*

# ── Dependencies & cruft ──
node_modules/
.DS_Store

# ephemeral atomic-write temp + advisory lock files
*.lock
*.tmp

# identity handles (PII) — gitignored; commit only the *.example
identities.local.json
